%% Data Flow Diagram - TrustyAI Service Operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant TASCtrl as TAS Controller
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant TAS as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant IS as InferenceService
    participant LMPod as LM-eval Pod<br/>+ driver sidecar
    participant S3 as S3/OCI Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP

    Note over User,PG: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment & Integration

    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>TASCtrl: Watch notification
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(trustyai-service + kube-rbac-proxy)
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service, Route, PVC/DB
    TASCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch InferenceService<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS env
    IS->>TAS: Forward payloads<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (internal certs)

    Note over User,PG: Flow 1b: External Client Access

    User->>Route: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS
    Route->>KRBP: Re-encrypt<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (serving certs)
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Auth result
    KRBP->>TAS: Proxy request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    TAS->>PG: Query/Store data<br/>5432/TCP (optional TLS)
    TAS-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS Response
    Route-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,PG: Flow 2: LMEvalJob Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>LMESCtrl: Watch notification
    LMESCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod<br/>(lm-eval + driver sidecar)
    LMPod->>IS: Model inference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS/gRPC
    LMPod->>S3: Download datasets / Upload results<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    LMPod->>K8sAPI: Status update<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,PG: Flow 3: GuardrailsOrchestrator Auto-Config

    User->>K8sAPI: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>GORCHCtrl: Watch notification
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Discover InferenceServices by label
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(orchestrator + gateway + detector)
    GORCHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Routes
